<p>
<note n="0719001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0719001">地獄畜生＝那落迦傍生【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0719002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0719002">〔世〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0720001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0720001">合＝略【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
